metadata.title: U.S. Chargé d’Affaires Natalie Baker calls on DPM Ishaq Dar

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Mar 11 (APP):U.S. Charge d'Affaires Natalie A. Baker Tuesday called on Deputy Prime Minister and Foreign Minister (DPM/FM), Senator Muhammad Ishaq Dar. The two sides, inter alia, agreed to upscale and strengthen economic and trade relations as well as cooperation in counterterrorism and security domains, a DPM Office news release said.
